text: Onchidina is a genus of air-breathing sea slugs, a shell-less marine pulmonate gastropod mollusks in the family Onchidiidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Onchidina include: * Onchidina australis J.E. Gray in Semper, 1885 * Onchidina guineensis (Labbé, 1934) ==References== Category:Onchidiidae
title: Onchidina
